ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (GIANT MINE) which provides for the withdrawal from disposal of the subsurface rights associated with the abandoned Giant Mine site in Yellowknife in order to allow for its remediation and to avoid potential conflicts with other users of that site.
